title: Rwanda Mining Production
description: Mining production in Rwanda decreased 52.60 percent in September of 2022 over the same month in the previous year. Mining Production in Rwanda averaged 10.43 percent from 2012 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 377.20 percent in July of 2022 and a record low of -72.90 percent in December of 2020. This page provides - Rwanda Mining Production- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: National Institute of Statistics of Rwanda
